16#include "absl/strings/match.h"

18#include "api/video_codecs/video_encoder.h"
19#include "media/base/codec.h"

25namespace webrtc {
26
27namespace {
28
29// This class wraps the internal factory and adds simulcast.
30class BuiltinVideoEncoderFactory : public VideoEncoderFactory {
31 public:
32 BuiltinVideoEncoderFactory()
33 : internal_encoder_factory_(new InternalEncoderFactory()) {}
34
35 VideoEncoderFactory::CodecInfo QueryVideoEncoder(
36 const SdpVideoFormat& format) const override {
37 // Format must be one of the internal formats.
38 RTC_DCHECK(
39 format.IsCodecInList(internal_encoder_factory_->GetSupportedFormats()));
40 VideoEncoderFactory::CodecInfo info;
41 return info;
42 }
43
44 std::unique_ptr<VideoEncoder> CreateVideoEncoder(
45 const SdpVideoFormat& format) override {
46 // Try creating internal encoder.
47 std::unique_ptr<VideoEncoder> internal_encoder;
48 if (format.IsCodecInList(
49 internal_encoder_factory_->GetSupportedFormats())) {
50 internal_encoder = std::make_unique<EncoderSimulcastProxy>(
51 internal_encoder_factory_.get(), format);
52 }
53
54 return internal_encoder;
55 }
56
57 std::vector<SdpVideoFormat> GetSupportedFormats() const override {
58 return internal_encoder_factory_->GetSupportedFormats();
59 }
60
61 private:
62 const std::unique_ptr<VideoEncoderFactory> internal_encoder_factory_;
63};
64
65} // namespace
66
67std::unique_ptr<VideoEncoderFactory> CreateBuiltinVideoEncoderFactory() {
68 return std::make_unique<BuiltinVideoEncoderFactory>();
69}
70
71} // namespace webrtc
